statements.sql: select `teams`.*, `periods`.`year`, `periods`.`semester` from `teams` inner join `periods` on `teams`.`id_period` = `periods`.`id` where `teams`.`is_active` = 1 order by `id_period` desc, `id` desc, `name` asc

select `team_categories`.`id_team`, `categories`.`name` from `team_categories` inner join `categories` on `team_categories`.`id_category` = `categories`.`id` inner join `teams` on `teams`.`id` = `team_categories`.`id_team` where `teams`.`is_active` = 1 order by `team_categories`.`id_team` desc, `categories`.`name` asc

select * from `team_documents` inner join `teams` on `teams`.`id` = `team_documents`.`id_team` where `teams`.`is_active` = 1 and `team_documents`.`deleted_at` is null order by `team_documents`.`id_team` asc, `team_documents`.`id_team_require_documents` asc, `team_documents`.`sort` asc
